description: Recording ID. Unique recording ID - a combination of media type, child ID, and month, e.g., video_41_12. See README or seedlings-nouns-codebook.csv for details.
Region start. Start of the region as the number of ms from the start of the audio file.
Does this interval belong to a subregion?
Does this interval belong to top 3 most talkative hours?
Does this interval belong to top 4 most talkative hours?
Is this interval part of surplus regions?
(Subregions only) Subregion position. Chronological position of the subregion. NA if not a subregion.
(Subregions only) Subregion rank. Rank of the subregion from 1 (highest) to 5 (lowest). NA if not a subregion.
